			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>When businesswoman gather together, amazing things happen. Just present them with a challenge and almost immediately, they will begin to work together to bring about a positive solution. Let us do what we can to support women business owners. Think about how you can contribute to their success in the work you already do. Can you make them more visible in the marketplace? Can you steer your network in their direction to support them financially? Do what you can, so women can support their families as well as their communities.</p>
<p>Join us on April 14th at our 2nd Annual Helping Women Succeed in Atlanta event. This spring empowerment summit will leave the women with information they can USE to leap to the next level in their business. In addition, the new connections will be priceless and the inspiration will be immeasurable! We look forward to seeing you there. Buy your tickets today. <a href="http://www.SupportWomen.eventbrite.com">http://www.SupportWomen.eventbrite.com</a></p>
