<li>Spelman College</li>
<li>DeKalb County Schools</li>
<li>Fulton County Schools</li>
<li>Georgia Department of Labor</li>
<li>American Public Transportation Association</li>
<li>Mercer University</li>
<li>Illinois Department of Human Services</li>
<li>Atlanta Housing Authority <em>and more</em></li>
</ul>
